Conversion issues

TODO:

  • report conversion errors to Saara (Trond, Steinar)
  • Have a look at the two suggestions for pdf discussed in the previous meeting (Saara)
    • implemented replacement of r vv with rvv. The source of the error is in pdf-conversion, where the space between r and double v is falsely interpreted as space-mark. This concerns only one document and only r and double v.
      • Comment: any initial double consonant is an indication of a space too much (no initial geminates in Sámi).
    • The hyphens in page breaks are now replaced with , although I’m still testing it.
